entries.s_426: I don't have anything at the moment.
entries.s_428: Very well. Return when you do.
entries.s_47a68e94: For instance, I pay dearly for the mystical tomes found off the Sayormi in the Dead Forest. Bring them to me, along with whatever else you find, and I shall pay you handsomely for them.
entries.s_5ceff11f: Greetings. [Kinaugha nods.] I deal in all things mystical; things you might find on your adventures. Bring them to me and I shall pass on wordly credits for them.
entries.s_e022ccee: Hmm.. I think I have some of those things for you.
